/*       MD036707 - FOOB in GLC44. Clear work file GLSYSOZX.         */
/*                  Apply for MD037302.                              */
/*       AR1097218A - GLC0720 seq 10001 failed Out of Balance        */
/*       CGL142 - Tactical COB changes GL                            */
/*       CGL120 - GL COB Components Task Split                       */
/*                                                                   */
